The file aims to teach you how to use the auto-deploy.

Note: The servers should be set mutual trust

The steps as blow:
1. change the file hostrc, set the storage_ip_list and the controller_ip.
   
2. Under the tool/manifest folder, if you have 3 storage nodes,
   you must create 3 folders for storage and 1 folder for controller.
   
3. put the vsm rpm packages under the vsmrepo folder if you don't make vsm from the source.

4. you can put the dependence folder named vsmrepo uder the tool folder, too. If you don't do it,
   it will try to connect the internet to download these dependence packages.

5. run the command "bash +x install.sh --help", it will show the usage information.


